Experiment mode is likely to be similar to the February long run but with the   
addition of scans towards Sondrestromfjord when the cusp is between the two   
radars.   
Approximately:   
Noon      Low elevation North   
Afternoon Sondrestromfjord scan   
Evening   CP2   
Midnight  CP4 (south)   
Morning   CP2   
With interleaved field every other 'minute', tau0 at 6.4s   

